<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Apollonopolis Magna</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Μάξιμος Τιναρσιεγέτι τῇ ἀδελφῇ πλεῖστα 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν καὶ διὰ παντὸς ὑγιαίνειν· 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐὰν ἔλθῃς εἰς τὰς ἡμέρας σου τοῦ <choice><corr>τεκεῖν</corr><sic>τεκιν</sic></choice>, γράψον μοι 

    <lb n="4"/><choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> εἰσέλθω καὶ τὴν λοχίαν σου ποιήσω, <choice><corr>ἐπεὶ</corr><sic>επι</sic></choice> οὐκ οἶ-

    <lb n="5"/>δά σου τὸν μῆνα. χάριν τούτου προέγραψά σοι, <choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="6"/>καὶ σὺ προλάβῃς καὶ γράψῃς μοι <choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> εἰσέλθω ἐν 

    <lb n="7"/>τῷ πλοίῳ τῶν κιβ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αρ</unclear>ίων <choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγὼ</corr><sic>καγω</sic></choice> <choice><corr>μείνω</corr><sic>μινω</sic></choice> ἐχόνομά 

    <lb n="8"/>σου καὶ τὴν λοχίαν <choice><corr>σου</corr><sic>μου</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ποιήσω</corr><sic>ποιησης</sic></choice>. σοὶ γὰρ προσέχω ὅτι 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐχόνομά σου <choice><corr>μενῶ</corr><sic>μεναω</sic></choice> <choice><corr>τεκεῖν</corr><sic>τεκιν</sic></choice>. ἐὰν μὴ πέμψῃς ἐπ᾽ ἐ-

    <lb n="10"/>μὲ οὐ χάριτάν μοι ποιεῖς. ἔμελλόν σοι πέμψαι 

    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>ἀγγεῖα</corr><sic>ανγια</sic></choice> εἰς τὴν λοχίαν σου· χάριν τούτου οὐκ <choice><corr>ἀπέστειλα</corr><sic>απεστιλα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="12"/><choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> <choice><corr>εἰσερχόμενος</corr><sic>εισερχομενη</sic></choice> ἐνέγκω καὶ <choice><corr>δύο</corr><sic>δυω</sic></choice> <num value="2"/> μάτια θερμίων. 

    <lb n="13"/>ὁ φέρων σοι τὸ ὄστρακον <choice><corr>συστρέφει</corr><sic>συνστρεφι</sic></choice> <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/> πρὸς ἐμέ. διὰ αὐτοῦ 

    <lb n="14"/>μὴ ἀμελήσῃς γράψαι περὶ τῆ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> κατ᾽ οἰκίας ἀπο-

    <lb n="15"/>γραφῆς. ἐφώνησάν σου τὸ ὄν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>μα καὶ οὐ προσ-

    <lb n="16"/><choice><corr>εφώνησαν</corr><sic>πρεσεφωνησαν</sic></choice>. ἔγραψα οὖν τῷ ἀδελφῷ σου ἄ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear>ω 

    <lb n="17"/><choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> καὶ τὸ ὄνομά σου προσδῷ σινεσωειστην. 

    <lb n="18"/>ἀσπαζόμεθά σε <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>αὶ Καλλέαν καὶ τοὺς 

    <lb n="19"/>ἐν οἴκῳ <choice><corr>πάντας</corr><sic>παντες</sic></choice> κατ᾽ ὄνομα. πέμψον μοι 

    <lb n="20"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">φ</unclear>ύ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>λα ὡς <choice><corr>εἰ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ς</supplied></corr><sic>ει</sic></choice> σ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">φυ</unclear>ρίδιον καὶ ποιήσω σοι 

    <lb n="21"/>αὐτὸ ἐπὶ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ου</unclear><gap extent="4" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ιωδω. 

    <lb n="22"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐρρῶ</supplied>σθαί σε εὔχομαι. </ab></div><div n="meta.74508" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Ostrakon</rs></p></div><div n="meta.74508" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="175" notBefore="176" type="textDate">Mitte - Ende II</date></p></div><div n="meta.74508" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Dossier eines Militärlagers in der Thebais. Zum Ort und zur Datierung vgl. BL IX, S. 385 und P.Hombert II, S. 9-13. Zu Z. 13 vgl. O.Krok. I 4,5 Anm.</p></div><div n="meta.74508" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">O.Florida</title><biblScope type="numbers">14</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">74508</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0027</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">14</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0027;;14" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.74508" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">518/519</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">385</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.74508" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Plate 8</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.74508" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translati